677
00:50:32.676 --> 00:50:34.178
Mis padres...

678
00:50:34.761 --> 00:50:36.054
...eran dos...

679
00:50:36.137 --> 00:50:39.140
...idealistas brillantes...

680
00:50:39.766 --> 00:50:41.059
